titleInfo.title: (N,N-DIMETHYLAMINOETHYL)CYCLOPENTADIENYL LIGAND IN COMPLEXATION OF TITANIUM AND ZIRCONIUM

mods.abstract: The first titanium(III, IV) and zirconium(IV) complexes containing the N,N-dimethylaminoethylcyclopentadienyl ligand have been synthesized following classical procedures. The coordination behaviour of the dimethylamino function is described on the basis of H-1-NMR and X-ray crystal structure informations.
